subject: Golf
lead_paragraph: Matt Bettencourt chipped in for an eagle, then scrambled down the stretch to shoot a four-under-par 68 for a one-stroke victory over Bob Heintz in the Reno-Tahoe Open, his first win on the PGA Tour.
